{"tid":1173720,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"陳奕迅嘅歌，太犀利了","createTime":"2019-05-27T10:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T04:31:05.000Z","uid":11127,"like":123,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7a778838fb2b22fd21e942bfd73b7d758aa342","tid":1173720,"uid":11127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:10:56.000Z","msg":"小學嗰陣，睇鋼之鍊金術師，你會聽不死傳說。<br />\n&mdash;若被傷害夠，就用一對手&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n中學嗰陣，體會到初戀嘅甜，你會聽幸福摩天輪。<br />\n&mdash;當生命似流連在摩天輪&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n大學嗰陣，回憶著校服嘅時光，你會聽粵語殘片。<br />\n&mdash;今天看這段歷史，像褪色午夜殘片&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n畢業嗰陣，想起單純的自己，你會聽我的快樂時代。<br />\n&mdash;長路漫漫，是如何走過&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n工作嗰陣，感慨用光陰換金錢，你會聽陀飛輪。<br />\n&mdash;為何用到盡了，至知哪樣緊要&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n中年嗰陣，與老友舉杯暢飲後，你會聽苦瓜。<br />\n&mdash;做人沒有苦澀可以嗎&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n孤單嗰陣，嘆息與舊友此情不再，你會聽最佳損友。<br />\n&mdash;問我有沒有，確實也沒有&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n婚宴嗰陣，見到當初的她穿上婚紗，你會聽阿牛。<br />\n&mdash;我，差點講真&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n晚年嗰陣，病得無力再青春一次，你會聽最後派對。<br />\n&mdash;活得精彩結尾，切勿流眼淚&mdash;"},{"pid":"cda9862c77daed75e3ffc07981ba635652d9a855","tid":1173720,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"死個一刻 一個靈魂的獨立<br />\n<br />\n死咗之後 活著多好"},{"pid":"d7c7680929b15c24567bfe63fcc880c670537ef4","tid":1173720,"uid":222406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"不良嗜好"},{"pid":"77c3eb75f092ef0ca670ec935b1b8c40bf41c259","tid":1173720,"uid":99725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"8949b65abb8e4144b9b57c6dfe4013beaff44aac","tid":1173720,"uid":26931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"分手既時候<br />\n<br />\n-流水很清楚惜花這個責任-<br />\n-尚有月台曾讓我們滿足到落淚-"},{"pid":"36ba984470c0a06e10acf4f8ce8e1e9dbf24c271","tid":1173720,"uid":11127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8949b65abb8e4144b9b57c6dfe4013beaff44aac","tid":1173720,"uid":26931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"分手既時候<br />\n<br />\n-流水很清楚惜花這個責任-<br />\n-尚有月台曾讓我們滿足到落淚-"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:37:50.000Z","msg":"是的 陳奕迅的歌還有說分手<br />\n上面沒有提及是因為我覺得一生中<br />\n會經歷太多次分開 很容易麻木 亦不開心<br />\n倒不如直接跳到阿牛 回憶單純快樂的時光"},{"pid":"00c9de9a982eba750e0648d7610bd5d2cddcf8e3","tid":1173720,"uid":59961,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"又唔係佢作"},{"pid":"c5f1cce26a660d43258d6e6b5b02cb664dbfcfa0","tid":1173720,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:46:00.000Z","msg":"工作既時候會聽24<br />\n做做做做 面對你不喜歡的東西 半日已流逝"},{"pid":"c5ea78465ef584098b7ca876556f0665498299db","tid":1173720,"uid":66514,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:47:48.000Z","msg":"有木有 有木有木有"},{"pid":"c1ec3f7879600fb091b2682b2ac559f6ea22c52a","tid":1173720,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:54:08.000Z","msg":"當你遇上一個 一個唔鐘意既人 既時候 ，明知無結果，但係就樂中其中， 你會聽無人止境"},{"pid":"83d790043cf3ae92932e7826bc037098d86f08c0","tid":1173720,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"唔應該"},{"pid":"77bbb1c98b2aa74ea2ed34ad4cc22c530cdd4191","tid":1173720,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c1ec3f7879600fb091b2682b2ac559f6ea22c52a","tid":1173720,"uid":123014,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:54:08.000Z","msg":"當你遇上一個 一個唔鐘意既人 既時候 ，明知無結果，但係就樂中其中， 你會聽無人止境"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"係咁打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99b6d99ee3ec412a1293e7c98c1bc09dcc1da1c","tid":1173720,"uid":90890,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"00c9de9a982eba750e0648d7610bd5d2cddcf8e3","tid":1173720,"uid":59961,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"又唔係佢作"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T10:57:21.000Z","ms